translate ru UnionKingdom1_9ea0e5cb:
    # "The trickle of guests continued."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom1_548fab62:
    # "So many faces, so many names. Nodding. Smiling."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom1_817c5c76:
    # "She had won her war. Subdued a rebellion."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom1_57618dce:
    # "Now they called her Regent. Some fools whispered Queen."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom1_18bc0a62:
    # "Now they called her Queen. A princess no more."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom1_f1da0b15:
    # "If she was so powerful, Sarah wondered why she often seemed to feel as if she lived at the mercy of her schedule."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom1_b6408150:
    # "Events to be planned. Council meetings to attend."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom1_e23bfc6c:
    # "There never seemed to be enough time in the day."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom1_3828e46a:
    # "Still, Sarah could only play at being frustrated. In truth she loved performing the role."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom1_307a5ac6:
    # "It made her proud to see the changes that came over the country by her hand. To see it flourish."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom1_39adbb18:
    # "And a part of her also hoped that somewhere her father might look down on her works and be proud."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom1_a45545d8:
    # "That reminded her. She had been so busy lately, she had let her prayers slip."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom1_75871ff3:
    # "Sarah was not a zealot by any means, perhaps not even fully religious, but a part of her did always hesitate about rejecting it altogether."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom1_ec598cdf:
    # "What was the harm in praying, after all. It would be, if anything, a brief moment of peace."
    ""

translate ru UnionKingdom1_20788c01:
    # "Then again, she had more than enough work to do as well."
    ""

